 g)\n* **Suscríbete a nuestro blog:** [https://blog.productmanagementsocie
 ty.com/](https://blog.productmanagementsociety.com/)\n* **Conecta con la f
 undadora:** [https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabrielanaumnik?utm_source=share_
 via&utm_content=profile&utm_medium=memb](https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabri
 elanaumnik?utm_source=share_via&utm_content=profile&utm_medium=memb)\n\n**
 *\n\n**Calling all Product People!** We're bringing together PMs\, founder
 s\, designers\, marketers\, and engineers for a relaxed evening of network
 ing. If you're in the product world or want to be\, come connect with your
  community!\n\n**What to expect:**\n**Interactive Icebreakers:** We’ll h
 elp you bypass the awkward small talk and start meaningful conversations e
