 /product-management-society/)\n* **Join our Slack channel:** [https://join
 .slack.com/t/product-mgmt-society/shared_invite/zt-2t477uzhc-0RWKnexUEQLmj
 lymeZ3_bg](https://join.slack.com/t/product-mgmt-society/shared_invite/zt-
 2t477uzhc-0RWKnexUEQLmjlymeZ3_bg)\n* **Subscribe to our blog:** [https://b
 log.productmanagementsociety.com/](https://blog.productmanagementsociety.c
 om/)\n* **Connect with the Founder:** [https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabriel
 anaumnik?utm_source=share_via&utm_content=profile&utm_medium=memb](https:/
 /www.linkedin.com/in/gabrielanaumnik?utm_source=share_via&utm_content=prof
 ile&utm_medium=memb)
